posting_body: ['Available for an **** AUGUST 1st or AUGUST 15th **** start date', 'Virtual tour available upon request', 'For rent is a gorgeous gut renovated 4 bed / 2 bath condo on the second floor of a multi family house on Fellsway West in Medford', '- New Everything', '- Big Bedrooms', '- Private Porche', '- Dishwasher', '- Laundry in basement', 'STREET PARKING ONLY - easy to find spots', 'Huge two floor unit with master bedroom and outdoor space.', 'Open living room and dining room, decorative fireplace, gleaming hardwood floors throughout.', 'New kitchen cabinets and brand new appliances as well as bathrooms featuring top of the line finishes.', 'Front and back deck on the second floor unit.', 'Make this gorgeous place your home!', 'Sorry No Pets Allowed', 'Utilities:', '- Tenants pay for their own separately metered gas & electric', 'Deposits:', '- First Months Rent, Last Months Rent & One Month Rent Security Deposit', 'Broker Fee:', '- One month rent broker fee due from incoming tenant', 'Brandon Keane', 'Licensed Real Estate Broker', 'Red Tree Real Estate', '193 Harvard St', 'Brookline MA 02446']
